'''Panayiotis Loizides''' is a Cypriot businessman. He has been the secretary-general of the Cyprus Chamber of Commerce and Industry since 1975, and the chairman of [[RCB Bank]].<ref>{{cite web|last=Lombardo |first=Germaine |url=http://ceoworld.biz/ceo/2012/06/08/interview-with-mr-panayiotis-loizides-secretary-general-cyprus-chamber-of-commerce-and-industry |title=Interview with Mr. Panayiotis Loizides, Secretary-General Cyprus Chamber of Commerce and Industry &#124; Chief Executive Forum |website=Ceoworld.biz |date=8 June 2012 |accessdate=4 April 2016}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.rcbcy.com/en/services/corporate/board/members/ |title=Members of the Board of Directors — RCB Bank Ltd |website=Rcbcy.com |date= |accessdate=4 April 2016}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|author=Panayiotis Loizides |url=https://www.bloomberg.com/research/stocks/private/person.asp?personId=313008999&privcapId=11001761&previousCapId=11001761&previousTitle=RCB%20Bank%20Ltd |title=Panayiotis Loizides: Executive Profile & Biography - Businessweek |website=Bloomberg.com |date= |accessdate=4 April 2016}}</ref>

